  priority: P1
  effort: xs
  description: |
    Three duplicate-claim incidents today (INFRA-1017, EFFECTIVE-023, INFRA-1016): I claimed gaps that another agent was already on. Pre-claim sweep today checks lock files and gap show only — it misses the two highest-signal duplicate indicators: (a) is there a /tmp worktree for this gap?, (b) is there an open PR with this gap-id in title? Both are cheap REST calls. Adding them would have saved 30+ min today and prevent operator confusion when 4 agents converge on the same hot gap.
