    - "scripts/coord/gap-preflight.sh adds two checks before declaring \"open and unclaimed\": (a) scan /private/tmp/chump-*<gap-id>* directories — if any exist, WARN with the path so the operator/agent can decide whether to resume or abort; (b) gh api repos/X/pulls?state=open + grep for <GAP-ID> in title — if any match, WARN with PR number"
