- id: INFRA-1111
  domain: INFRA
  title: ZERO-WASTE — chump_gh exponential backoff on 'rate limit already exceeded' response
  status: in_flight
  priority: P1
  effort: s
  description: |
    Today: when secondary rate-limit fires, scripts immediately retry — burning
    budget faster. Need detection + cooldown. Pairs with INFRA-1103 (throttle
    prevents most hits) — this catches the residual that slip through (e.g.,
    bursts from sibling sessions before throttle window updates).
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "scripts/coord/lib/github.sh chump_gh detects secondary-rate-limit (stderr contains \"rate limit already exceeded\" or \"You have exceeded a secondary rate limit\")"
    - "On detection: sleep with exponential backoff (1s, 2s, 4s, 8s, max 30s), then retry; up to 4 retries"
    - "After retry exhaustion: emit kind=gh_secondary_limit_hit with {script, api, retries, total_waited_ms} and return non-zero"
    - Per-script bypass via CHUMP_GH_NO_RETRY=1
    - "Unit test: 7/7 pass (scripts/ci/test-infra-1111-gh-backoff.sh)"
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

- id: INFRA-1112
  domain: INFRA
  title: ZERO-WASTE — separate mutation budget in chump_gh throttle (writes get tighter cap)
  status: done
  priority: P1
  effort: s
  description: |
    GitHub secondary rate limit is dramatically tighter on mutations than reads.
    Single 60/min cap is too loose for mutations (causes pr merge cascade failures)
    and too tight for reads (wastes throughput on innocuous polling).
    
    _chump_gh_classify_call() inspects gh argv to detect write operations.
    _chump_gh_throttle_wait() accepts api_class param; uses class-specific
    window file and cap. chump_gh() classifies before throttling.
  acceptance_criteria:
    - _chump_gh_classify_call reads gh argv to classify call as mutation vs query
    - "Mutations: pr merge/create/review/comment/edit; issue create/close/edit/comment; api -X POST/PATCH/PUT/DELETE"
    - "Default mutation cap: 15/min (CHUMP_GH_MUTATION_MAX=15). Default query cap: 60/min (CHUMP_GH_QUERY_MAX=60)"
    - "Separate window files: .gh-throttle-window.mutation + .gh-throttle-window.query"
    - "Emit kind=gh_self_throttled gains api_class: mutation|query field"
  closed_pr: 1808
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

