    - "Feature-gate: CHUMP_A2A_LAYER=0 (default) preserves today file-only behavior; CHUMP_A2A_LAYER=1 enables NATS-primary subscribe path"
    - "Release gate: 7-day single-host fleet run with CHUMP_A2A_LAYER=1, zero fleet_a2a_degraded events, subscriber latency p99 < 50ms verified in CI"
  notes: |
