    - "Tracing: `a2a_rpc_started` and `a2a_rpc_finished` (with `latency_ms`, `method`, `target_session`) registered in EVENT_REGISTRY.yaml and emitted on every RPC round-trip"
    - "Release gate: 7-day fleet run with `CHUMP_A2A_LAYER=2` sustaining > 10 RPCs/min, zero `a2a_rpc_handler_crashed` events, single-hop p99 < 50ms local"
