    - Help output non-empty, exit 0, summarizes purpose + key flags
    - scripts/ci/test-chump-subcommand-help.sh asserts all 6 leaf verbs (chump claim, chump ship, chump gap ship, chump gap preflight, chump gap decompose, chump gap triage) return exit 0 with usage strings (no LLM fallthrough, no missing-positional error)
