  title: "CREDIBLE: chump fleet brief reports Pillars=0/0/0/0 (of 0 pickable) when 17 INFRA gaps actually pickable — metric source misaligned"
  status: done
  priority: P1
  effort: s
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "Live evidence (2026-05-15 ~19:48 UTC SessionStart hook): \"Pillars: EFFECTIVE=0 CREDIBLE=0 RESILIENT=0 ZERO-WASTE=0  (of 0 pickable)\" while the local state.db reported 17 pickable INFRA P0/P1 xs"
