    - cargo-test-required (the gating job) needs both — but skips slow cleanly when fast fails so the failure surfaces in <3min instead of 15min
    - "Measure baseline: timing of fast tier alone (target <3min) vs combined (current 10-15min)"
    - "CI test scripts/ci/test-cargo-test-tiered.sh asserts the two jobs exist and the needs: chain is correct"
    - "docs/process/CI_LANES.md gains a \"fast vs slow test tiering\" section"
