    - "Telemetry: ambient kind=stale_gap_state_observed should drop to ~0 after this lands. Add scheduled audit (chump audit-status-drift, daily) that grep-checks every status=done gap has at least one PROOF_* row; flags violations as ambient kind=gap_status_unproven."
    - "Pairs with INFRA-1323 (local merge queue) — both must land before CHUMP_GITHUB_MODE=offline is operationally viable. ORDERING: this gap can ship before or after INFRA-1323; if it ships first the offline path inherits proof discipline; if it ships after the local-merge-queue.sh writes proof rows from day one."
