    - "Operator can configure per-repo: enable/disable, agent budget, fallback behavior"
    - "Audit log: every auto-resolved conflict is logged with both pre-state and post-state diffs for operator review"
    - "CI test: synthetic conflict scenario, verify agent resolves, verify no side's changes dropped, verify resolution passes tests"
  notes: |
    MARCUS M-C (daily-tax killer). Promoted P2→P1 2026-05-16. Marcus Q2 single biggest time-sink: 45 min of intense mental focus per PR rebase. Self-contained; can ship parallel to M-B.
