- id: INFRA-1521
  domain: INFRA
  title: "RESILIENT: docs-delta pre-commit hook reads wrong COMMIT_EDITMSG path in linked worktrees"
  status: open
  priority: P2
  effort: s
  description: |
    The docs-delta pre-commit hook at scripts/git-hooks/pre-commit (or a sub-script it calls) reads $REPO_ROOT/.git/COMMIT_EDITMSG to inspect the commit message during the hook. In a linked worktree, .git is a FILE (a gitdir pointer), not a directory, so the path $REPO_ROOT/.git/COMMIT_EDITMSG does not exist. The correct path is $(git rev-parse --git-dir)/COMMIT_EDITMSG which resolves to .git/worktrees/<name>/COMMIT_EDITMSG in a linked worktree.
    
    Symptom: CHUMP_DOCS_DELTA_CHECK=0 was required on every commit in every linked worktree throughout the 2026-05-16 session to avoid hook failures.
    
    Fix: replace the hardcoded $REPO_ROOT/.git/COMMIT_EDITMSG path with $(git rev-parse --git-dir)/COMMIT_EDITMSG in the relevant hook script.
    
    AC:
    - Linked worktree commit (e.g. in /private/tmp/chump-infra-*) succeeds without CHUMP_DOCS_DELTA_CHECK=0
    - Main worktree commit behavior unchanged
    - CI test: scripts/ci/test-docs-delta-linked-worktree.sh creates a linked worktree, makes a commit, asserts hook exits 0
  acceptance_criteria:
    - Hook script(s) that read $REPO_ROOT/.git/COMMIT_EDITMSG (or .git/COMMIT_EDITMSG) replaced with $(git rev-parse --git-dir)/COMMIT_EDITMSG
    - "Affected files: scripts/git-hooks/pre-commit and any sub-scripts it sources (grep `COMMIT_EDITMSG` across scripts/git-hooks/ to enumerate)"
    - Linked-worktree commit succeeds without CHUMP_DOCS_DELTA_CHECK=0 — verified by `cd /private/tmp/<linked-worktree>` + commit a doc-affecting change
    - Main-worktree commit behavior unchanged — same hook resolves to .git/COMMIT_EDITMSG via git rev-parse
    - "Smoke test scripts/ci/test-docs-delta-linked-worktree.sh: creates temp linked worktree, makes a commit that triggers docs-delta logic, asserts hook exits 0 AND that the message file was actually read (verify via debug log or stdout marker)"
    - Existing pre-commit tests in scripts/ci/ still pass
    - "Cross-link: workaround was CHUMP_DOCS_DELTA_CHECK=0 on every commit during 2026-05-16 session — landing this kills the workaround"
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

