    (d) /v2/?view=cockpit URL: decide whether to (i) keep as backward-compat alias to /v2/?cadence=now or (ii) drop. Default: keep for one release; emit deprecation console.warn. Document in PR.
    (e) Smoke verification: open /v2/ (no query), confirm cockpit renders. Open /v2/?view=cockpit, confirm cockpit renders (with or without deprecation warning, per decision (d)).
    
