    - Action runs INFRA-1591 snapshot suite against PR branch
    - Renders side-by-side baseline + PR-version + diff overlay images for each diff > 0%
    - "Posts/updates a single PR comment (no spam) with markdown table: view / viewport / pixel delta / diff image"
    - Comment footer includes re-baseline command + artifact link
    - Graceful no-op with warning comment if INFRA-1591 not yet wired (forward-compatible)
    - docs/process/PWA_VISUAL_DIFF_BOT.md documents action + reading the comment + adding views
  depends_on: [INFRA-1591]
