  description: |
    We are failing at gap metadata quality. 486 of 540 gaps (90%) have no opened_date field. The P0 aging census in CLAUDE.md Mission Driver and chump gap audit-priorities relies on opened_date to compute "age" — but audit-priorities shows every P0 as '0d old' because state.db was freshly imported and has no age data.
    
