    Multiple pre-existing main-state failures (INFRA-1287 orphans, INFRA-682 skills-bundle missing from path-filter, DOC-026 missing env-var allowlist entries, INFRA-1274 missing raw-gh allowlist for pr-failure-auto-rescue.sh, INFRA-306 canonical comment) squeaked through during 2026-05-20 — each blocked every subsequent PR until manually surgically fixed. Need a watchdog that catches main-red automatically and files a P0 so the next operator session inherits the diagnostic.
  acceptance_criteria:
