    Phase 3 Evangelism gap from the multi-agent-factory ingestion-engine review (2026-05-22). New users miss valuable primitives (chump-coord watch, chump gap consolidate, chump revert, PWA, the skills layer) because there is no curated showcase doc. The Evangelist content bot (META-066) will draft material for this surface once running, but no SPEC exists for what gets surfaced or how the doc is structured. Rough shape: (a) docs/HIDDEN_GEMS.md as the user-facing surface with structured sections (CLI commands, agent tools, config knobs, hidden features); (b) scripts/dev/build-hidden-gems.sh auto-populates skeleton from chump skill list + scripts/README.md catalog + chump-mcp.json + ambient EVENT_REGISTRY.yaml; (c) docs/HIDDEN_GEMS_CURATED.yaml operator overlay for hand-picked entries auto-merged into the rendered doc; (d) refreshed via hourly planner or daily cron skill; (e) Evangelist bot reads HIDDEN_GEMS.md as input for blog/evangelism content (closes the loop with META-066).
