  title: "CREDIBLE: measure local-preflight vs CI agreement rate — emit kind=preflight_ci_agreement {gap_id, preflight_pass, ci_pass} per PR; weekly rollup catches preflight-theater (false-negatives) and preflight-overreach (false-positives) — currently 0 visibility into whether the <60s local gate matches the 10-12min CI gate"
