- id: INFRA-2016
  domain: INFRA
  title: "EFFECTIVE P1: Claude Code PreToolUse hook auto-reads inbox + prepends CRIT messages to next-tool context"
  status: done
  priority: P0
  effort: m
  description: |
    The 'fast AF + non-destructive' path the operator wants. Phase 3
    of the live-A2A design.
    
    INFRA-2014 = interrupt via tmux send-keys (destructive — stops the
    agent mid-flight)
    INFRA-2016 = inject as context via PreToolUse hook (non-destructive
    — agent finishes current action then sees interrupt before next)
    
    Both can coexist:
    - EMERGENCY → tmux send-keys C-c (INFRA-2014)
    - CRIT      → PreToolUse hook injection (INFRA-2016)
    - WARN      → ambient emit (workers in loop tick)
    - INFO      → inbox file (next session)
    
    Trade-off: hook adds ~50-200ms per Nth tool call (the chump-inbox.sh
    --check-urgent call). Worth it — operator gets "magical" delivery
    without violating mid-tool isolation.
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "New .claude/hooks/pre-tool-use-inbox-check.sh: invoked every CHUMP_INBOX_HOOK_INTERVAL tool calls (default 10); calls chump-inbox.sh check-urgent; if any unread CRIT message, hook stdout contains the message as <inbox-interrupt> XML block which Claude Code injects into next-tool context"
    - Hook registered in .claude/settings.json under hooks.PreToolUse matching Bash|Edit|Write tools
    - "Non-destructive: agent finishes current tool, then BEFORE next tool sees the inbox interrupt as additional context; can choose to read fully + reply OR continue but ack later"
    - Counter state in .chump-locks/<session>-tool-counter.txt — increments per tool call, resets when inbox is read or every hour
    - Inbox-cursor advance happens when the hook surfaces a message (so re-running the hook doesn't loop)
    - "Smoke test scripts/ci/test-inbox-hook-injection.sh: simulate 11 tool calls with one CRIT message in inbox; assert hook fires once at call 10 + injects message; counter resets"
    - "Doc update: .claude/README.md + docs/process/CLAUDE_GOTCHAS.md — 'live inbox-on-tool' pattern"
  closed_date: '2026-05-29'
  closed_pr: 2613
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

