- id: INFRA-2026
  domain: INFRA
  title: "RESILIENT P1: post-push PR integrity daemon — auto-reopen on stale-base force-close"
  status: done
  priority: P1
  effort: xs
  description: |
    Incident 2026-05-25T19:00Z: wizard pushed stale main HEAD to
    chump/infra-1974-claim via force-with-lease from a stale worktree.
    GitHub auto-closed PR #2582 because the pushed SHA was already on main.
    Manual recovery (git reflog + gh pr reopen) worked but cost ~15 min
    and risked silent data loss.
    
    Fix: 60s daemon that scans for closed (not merged) chump/* PRs within
    a rolling 120s window, auto-reopens them, and broadcasts CRIT to the
    fleet so all agents are aware of the incident.
    
    Detection heuristic: gh pr list --state closed filtered to chump/*
    branches + closedAt within window + stateReason != MERGED. This catches
    the stale-base auto-close pattern without touching the pre-push hook
    (separate concern, INFRA-2005 in parallel).
    
    Telemetry:
      post_push_auto_close_recovered — recovery action taken
      post_push_integrity_watch_ok   — clean scan heartbeat
      post_push_integrity_watch_err  — daemon config/API error
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "New scripts/coord/post-push-integrity-watch.sh: runs every 60s; queries gh pr list --state closed for chump/* branches; detects PRs closed (not merged) within 120s; logs INCIDENT + in non-dry-run mode calls gh pr reopen"
    - "On incident: emits kind=post_push_auto_close_recovered to ambient.jsonl with pr, branch, state_reason, reopen_status fields"
    - "On incident: calls scripts/coord/broadcast-urgent.sh --urgency CRIT fleet-wide with incident summary"
    - "On clean scan: emits kind=post_push_integrity_watch_ok with checked and incidents counts"
    - "On gh/config error: emits kind=post_push_integrity_watch_err with reason field"
    - "New scripts/setup/install-post-push-integrity-launchd.sh: installs com.chump.post-push-integrity launchd plist with 60s StartInterval + RunAtLoad=true; uses resolve-main-worktree so plist survives worktree reaping (INFRA-451)"
    - scripts/coord/fleet-autopilot.sh AUTOPILOT_LAYERS includes com.chump.post-push-integrity entry
    - scripts/setup/optional-installers-allowlist.txt includes install-post-push-integrity-launchd.sh
    - Event kinds registered in scripts/ci/event-registry-reserved.txt
    - "scripts/ci/test-post-push-integrity.sh: 8 tests covering no-PRs/watch_ok, NOT_PLANNED incident detection, MERGED skip, non-chump branch skip, out-of-window skip, bash -n syntax — all pass"
  closed_date: '2026-05-29'
  closed_pr: 2615
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

