    - "Smoke test scripts/ci/test-gap-sync.sh: synth fixture with 4 drift patterns (YAML-only, DB-only, TODO-AC overwrite, title divergence); assert --check non-zero with all 4; assert --pull recovers DB to YAML; assert --push fills the missing YAML; assert post-recovery --check exits 0; assert --dry-run mutates nothing"
