tial discovery* surface. They're complementary, not duplicates. Harvester is internal-only; this is external-first-touch.\n- Discovered during: ehippy/derelict demo on 2026-05-28, where I picked a demo-safe /health endpoint instead of engaging with ideas/TODO.md's \"Next 6 Features\" list. Patrick's real next step is character.router + frontend creation form; we shipped a generic health probe."
