    - "Unit tests in external_repo_schema.rs: (a) round-trip snapshot save/load, (b) round-trip scan save/load, (c) signal-append produces well-formed JSONL one-per-line, (d) reject malformed tag (e.g. 'external:foo/bar' missing the _repo, 'external_repo:foo' missing the slash). cargo fmt + cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings + cargo test GREEN. Voice-lint clean. PR via scripts/coord/bot-merge.sh --auto-merge."
