    - "One-shot migration at recorder startup: UPDATE events SET gap_id='' WHERE gap_id IS NULL; same for session_id and subject; idempotent (CHECK that the column has any NULLs first to avoid UNIQUE collisions per ts_ms,session_id,event_kind,gap_id)"
    - "Smoke test extends scripts/ci/test-fleet-recorder.sh: emit a chump-coord event with no gap_id, assert the resulting row has gap_id='' not NULL"
    - cargo fmt + cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings + cargo check --workspace GREEN; chump preflight before push
