  description: |
    webkit2gtk-4.1 is a transitional package that existed in Ubuntu 22.04 jammy but was dropped in Ubuntu 24.04 noble. ubuntu-latest is now 24.04. The package is referenced in 7 separate apt-get install blocks in ci.yml (fast-checks, clippy, cargo-test, coverage, e2e-pwa, audit, tauri-cowork-e2e jobs). When runner pools fully migrate to noble these blocks will fail with 'E: Unable to locate package webkit2gtk-4.1'. Fix: replace webkit2gtk-4.1 with libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0 in each block (or remove the transitional line if libwebkit2gtk-4.1-dev already depends on libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0). Evidence: packages.ubuntu.com/noble/webkit2gtk-4.1 returns no such package; libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0 and libwebkit2gtk-4.1-dev both exist in noble. Audit source: docs/audits/CI_DEPENDENCY_AUDIT_2026-05-30.md (META-177 lane B, INFRA-2290).
