      EMITTER (works):    disk-health-monitor (5min cron) → emits disk_critical to ambient.jsonl
      EMITTER (works):    disk-pressure-watchdog (15min cron) → emits disk_critical to ambient.jsonl
      REAPER  (works):    disk-pressure-reaper --execute (15min cron) → tier 1-4 escalation
