      PAGER   (exists):   scripts/dispatch/operator-recall.sh — halt-class pager
      ────────────────────── BREAKS HERE ──────────────────────
      disk_critical event has ZERO ambient consumers that ACT on it
      reaper runs on a FIXED 15min cron, not reactive to the alert
