- id: INFRA-2313
  domain: INFRA
  title: META-225 daemon-activator extension — git-show fallback for BOT scripts (not just installers) when local copy missing
  status: open
  priority: P1
  effort: xs
  description: |
    META-225 cascade demonstrated a gap on first live run: when a freshly-merged install-*.sh script references a BOT script (e.g. install-ghost-pr-closer.sh references scripts/coord/ghost-pr-closer.sh), the installer's own preflight 'BOT_SCRIPT not found — must land first' guard exits 2 BEFORE the daemon-activator's git-show extraction fallback (AC #1) can run. Result: install-ghost-pr-closer.sh + install-main-worktree-drift-detector.sh both FAILed on 2026-05-30 18:55Z cascade despite META-225 having merged at 18:46Z. Manual workaround: shepherd ran git show origin/main:scripts/coord/<botname>.sh into the worktree, then re-ran installers — both succeeded. The auto-fix: daemon-activator should ALSO extract referenced bot scripts when missing, OR the installers themselves should switch from 'exit 2 if not found' to 'git show origin/main:<path> > <local>' on missing.
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "Option A (preferred): scripts/coord/daemon-activator-loop.sh adds a pre-install step that parses BOT_SCRIPT= line from the installer; if the referenced path doesn't exist locally, runs git show origin/main:<bot_script_path> > <local_path> + chmod +x BEFORE invoking the installer"
    - "Option B (acceptable fallback): all META-225-style installers (install-stale-pr-rebase-bot.sh as reference) replace 'echo ERROR + exit 2' on missing bot script with a git-show-or-fail block; preserves manual-invocation safety while unblocking cascade"
    - scripts/ci/test-quartermaster-auto-fixers.sh gains a new assertion (g) — synthetic main with fresh install + bot script, only installer on local disk, asserts cascade succeeds via extraction
    - "Doctrine: docs/process/SHEPHERD_AUTONOMY_LADDER.md gains note about this discovery + the dirty-main-worktree fallback being recursive (installer fallback PLUS bot-script fallback)"
    - On ship, run cascade locally and verify both ghost-pr-closer + main-worktree-drift-detector activate without manual git-show extraction
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

