    - "Smoke verifications: `chump inventory show scripts/coord/trunk-sentinel-daemon.sh` correctly attributes PR #2916 / INFRA-2324; `chump inventory pr 2916` lists ≥3 artifacts; `chump inventory class-stats` shows `unknown` activation_state at ≤20% of total artifacts (was 61%)"
    - "Failure-class taxonomy: TRANSIENT (REST 503 fetching merge commit; retried) vs PERMANENT (commit not on main; logged as unlinkable_provenance); ambient kinds emitted: provenance_fallback (transient), backfill_unlinkable (permanent)"
    - Smoke test scripts/ci/test-inventory-v2-calibration.sh covers BUG-1 via synthetic out-of-order merge timestamps + verifies graph-walk picks the right PR
