- id: INFRA-2522
  domain: INFRA
  title: "RESILIENT P1: collapse local commit/push gates — 2021-line pre-commit (45 blocks) + 1307-line pre-push (48 blocks) down to ~3 fast local checks (fmt, cargo check, identity/claim); move all depth to CI"
  status: done
  priority: P1
