  acceptance_criteria:
    - "pre-commit + pre-push each enforce <=3 fast checks (target <10s total): formatting, compile/syntax, claim/identity"
    - every other current block-point (obs-budget, rust-first, redundancy, ac-completeness, registry-coverage, preflight-parity, bypass-trailer, etc.) moves to CI as a single parallel job OR is deleted
