- id: INFRA-2628
  domain: INFRA
  title: "RESILIENT P0: session clock-in/clock-out + main-freshness enforcement — prevent stale-base regressions like RESILIENT-058 nearly rescinding INFRA-2524"
  status: done
  priority: P2
  effort: m
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "Today 2026-06-03 RESILIENT-058 Sonnet dispatched worktree was created against main HEAD ~56e15def while INFRA-2524 had landed at 31e71d16 — Sonnet rebased AWAY a 66-line fail-open guard. Caught by orchestrator before push but if missed would have re-broken fail-open behavior on next garbled-watchdog tick. Operator: we keep working on the wrong main."
    - "Fix-A: chump session start emits kind=session_opened with current origin/main HEAD sha and pid; chump session end emits kind=session_closed. Stored in .chump-locks/.session-clock.jsonl for cross-session visibility."
    - "Fix-B: chump claim refuses if local origin/main is more than CHUMP_MAIN_STALE_THRESHOLD_S (default 600s) behind remote — auto-fetches first OR fails with clear message pointing to git fetch origin main"
    - "Fix-C: pre-push hook also checks main-freshness; refuses push if branch was last-rebased against a main HEAD that is now N commits behind current remote origin/main HEAD (with N tunable, default 5). Emits kind=stale_rebase_blocked with old-base/current-base/commits-behind"
    - "Fix-D: launchd daemon com.chump.main-freshness-watcher tick every 60s broadcasts kind=fleet_main_head_updated when origin/main HEAD changes, including the new sha and merged-commit-list. Sessions can subscribe."
    - "Regression test scripts/ci/test-stale-main-guards.sh covers: (a) claim against stale main blocked, (b) push against stale-rebased branch blocked, (c) main-head-updated event fires on fetch detecting new HEAD, (d) session_opened+session_closed bracket properly"
  notes: |
    [2026-06-03T23:58:34Z] confirmed on origin/main (merged fix commit); mission-loop registry hygiene
  closed_pr: 2999
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

- id: INFRA-2629
  domain: INFRA
  title: "RESILIENT P0: last-mile rescuer daemon — catch orphan commits + unpushed branches + dispatched-agent-stalled work before they're abandoned"
  status: done
  priority: P2
  effort: m
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "[\n\"Today 2026-06-03 RESILIENT-058 Sonnet committed bd5457680 locally then lease expired without push; orphan-worktree-watchdog emitted kind=orphan_worktree_detected but no consumer existed to act. Earlier in same session, orchestrator-opus 5h gap left INFRA-2458 commit (e5358cf42) and INFRA-2484 commit (7ae7d5bb3) in /tmp worktrees never pushed until manual recovery. Operator: a lot of work gets dropped before the finish line.\",\n\"BUILD ON existing prior art: orphan-worktree-watchdog.sh (RESILIENT-026, detects abandoned worktrees, emits kind=orphan_worktree_detected) + stale-pr-rebase-bot.sh (INFRA-2295, rebases open PRs) already exist. The hole: orphan-worktree-watchdog notifies but no one acts.\",\n\"NEW scripts/coord/last-mile-rescuer.sh + .chump/launchd/com.chump.last-mile-rescuer.plist (tick every 120s) — CONSUMER side of the existing detection.\",\n\"Trigger 1: subscribe to kind=orphan_worktree_detected ambient events in last 10 min. For each: re-verify (worktree still exists, branch has commits ahead of origin/main, no PR open). If verified: rebase onto fresh origin/main; push via bot-merge.sh; emit kind=last_mile_rescue_completed.\",\n\"Trigger 2: scan local branches matching chump/(INFRA"
    - RESILIENT
    - EFFECTIVE
    - CREDIBLE
    - ZERO
    - META
    - COG
    - "MISSION)-[0-9]+-claim. For each: same verify + rescue.\",\n\"Trigger 3: scan ambient for kind=sub_agent_dispatched events older than CHUMP_LAST_MILE_AGENT_STALL_S (default 1800s) without matching PR opened — emit kind=last_mile_agent_stall_detected.\",\n\"Operator audit gate: dry-run mode CHUMP_LAST_MILE_DRY_RUN=1 only emits intent events without actually pushing — for first deploy verification.\",\n\"Regression test scripts/ci/test-last-mile-rescuer.sh: synthetic orphan-worktree-detected event + branch with commits + no PR → assert rescuer triggered + (dry-run) push intent emitted; clean branch with open PR → assert skipped.\"\n]"
  closed_pr: 2998
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

