- id: INFRA-2655
  domain: INFRA
  title: "RESILIENT P0: audit.yml audit-required missing if:always() — INFRA-2565 matrix-shard refactor regression caught by INFRA-2191 ruleset guard"
  status: done
  priority: P2
  effort: m
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "INFRA-2452 (PR #2973) moved audit and audit-required from ci.yml to audit.yml. INFRA-2191 test scripts/ci/test-ruleset-doc-only-pr.sh still points CI_YML at .github/workflows/ci.yml — so the if: always() assertion fails because audit-required is no longer in ci.yml."
    - "Caught when #2998 (INFRA-2629) PR triggered the test inside the audit-required job context — testing itself by looking in the wrong place."
    - "Fix: scripts/ci/test-ruleset-doc-only-pr.sh should look in audit.yml (audit-required is now there). Either change CI_YML to audit.yml, OR scan both files and use whichever contains the audit-required job."
