  description: |
    EVAL-101 closed as a null result (Δ=+0.025) but violated multiple RESEARCH_INTEGRITY.md
    requirements. The preregistration (docs/eval/preregistered/EVAL-101.md) specified:
    - Agent under test: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 (Anthropic API)
