    - All 6 new env vars (CHUMP_FRESHNESS_COMMITS_THRESHOLD, CHUMP_FRESHNESS_BINARY_AGE_S, CHUMP_FRESHNESS_STALE_COMMITS, CHUMP_FRESHNESS_STALE_BINARY_AGE_S, CHUMP_FRESHNESS_DISABLE_FETCH, CHUMP_ACCEPT_STALE) documented in scripts/ci/env-vars-internal.txt under META-115 header
    - NEW Pattern 12 in docs/process/SHEPHERD_LOOP_PLAYBOOK.md (Verify-at-source via freshness preamble) documents the workflow with the 2026-05-27 shepherd 3-stale-false-positive precedent (recovery-queue-emit.sh phantom-missing + fleet-hold-check.sh + chump --temp multi-line)
    - Smoke test scripts/ci/test-freshness-preamble.sh covers (1) file existence, (2) default invocation, (3) simulated STALE via binary-age threshold override, (4) simulated CRITICAL_STALE, (5) gate refusal exit=2, (6) gate bypass with ambient audit emit, (7) valid --json output, (8) env-vars-internal.txt + event-registry-reserved.txt allowlisting; test sets CHUMP_AMBIENT_DISABLE=1 + CHUMP_FRESHNESS_DISABLE_FETCH=1 for hermeticity; exit 0 required
    - "Phase 1 NON-GOALS (deferred to follow-up sub-gaps): SessionStart hook wiring at ~/.claude/hooks/SessionStart.sh; chump fleet-bootstrap --check integration; per-event kind registration in EVENT_REGISTRY.yaml; chump CLI subcommand wrapper (`chump freshness check`)"
