- id: META-123
  domain: META
  title: "[UMBRELLA] External-repo first-touch flow — 7-role pipeline (Scout → Decompose → External-collab → Target → Handoff → Shepherd → Context-Keeper) + chump onboard CLI"
  status: done
  priority: P1
  effort: l
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "UMBRELLA per docs/strategy/MARKET_POSITIONING_2026-05-27.md Bet-1 + Bet-2 + Marcus M-B/M-C arc.\n\nProblem statement (discovered during ehippy/derelict demo on 2026-05-28): chump has no first-touch flow for an external repo. When the operator says \"demo chump on this repo,\" there's no role that reads the repo's intent (TODO/README/IMPLEMENTATION/commits/issues), proposes a backlog grounded in the maintainer's roadmap, and threads it through the existing curator-* lanes. The demo defaults to generic tasks (e.g. /health endpoint) instead of engaging the maintainer's roadmap.\n\n7-role pipeline:\n  Scout (NEW) → Decompose (exists) → External-collab (exists) → Target (exists) →\n  Handoff (exists) → Shepherd (exists) → Context-Keeper (NEW or Harvester ext)\n\nChild gaps to file:\n  - INFRA-NNNN curator-opus-scout role definition + agent spec (.claude/agents/curator-opus-scout.md)\n  - INFRA-NNNN `chump onboard <repo-url-or-path>` CLI (already filed as INFRA-2108 — re-scope as child)\n  - INFRA-NNNN ExternalRepoContract typed handoff (crates/chump-handoff/src/contracts.rs)\n  - INFRA-NNNN curator-opus-decompose `--external-repo` flag\n  - INFRA-NNNN curator-opus-target picker filter for external_repo: tag\n  - INFRA-NNNN curator-opus-shepherd fork-aware PR rescue\n  - INFRA-NNNN curator-opus-context-keeper role (OR Harvester external mode)\n  - INFRA-NNNN ~/.chump/external/<owner>/<repo>/ scan + delta + memory schema\n\nVerify (end-to-end demo target):\n  $ chump onboard https://github.com/ehippy/derelict\n  [scout] cloned to ~/.chump/external/ehippy/derelict\n  [scout] read: README, CLAUDE.md, ideas/TODO.md (Next 6 Features), 20 recent commits, 0 open issues\n  [scout] proposing 8 gaps (3 high-confidence, 4 med, 1 low)\n  [scout] surfacing to external-collab review queue\n  ...\n  (operator approves 3)\n  [target] claimed external/ehippy/derelict/character-router-mutation\n  [handoff] dispatched via CodeFixContract to chump worker\n  [worker] shipped 1 PR to repairman29:derelict (head=character-create-mutation, base=ehippy:main)\n  [shepherd] PR opened, watching for review\n\nThat's the demo. Today none of this exists. Filing as umbrella; decompose at claim time.\n\nCross-references:\n  - INFRA-1318 Liaison Phase 2 (continuous webhook surface) — complementary, not duplicate\n  - INFRA-2108 chump onboard CLI (re-scope as child)\n  - META-069 dispatch defaults (Opus vs Sonnet) — Target step applies this\n  - META-027 sub-agent dispatch (existing pattern)\n  - Marcus M-B canonical demo arc — this IS the canonical demo"
