- id: META-272
  domain: META
  title: "ZERO-WASTE: Cold Water adversarial audit outputs stranded — RED_LETTER Issues 12 and 13 never reached origin/main"
  status: open
  priority: P1
  effort: s
  description: |
    RED_LETTER Issues #12 (2026-05-18) and #13 (2026-05-25) were committed to a
    detached HEAD in the Cold Water execution environment but never pushed to origin/main.
    origin/main's RED_LETTER.md contains only Issue #11 as of 2026-06-01.
    
    Evidence:
    - `git show origin/main:docs/audits/RED_LETTER.md | grep "^## Issue"` → only "## Issue #11"
    - `git log HEAD ^origin/main -- docs/audits/RED_LETTER.md` → commit 1e1ca3c (2026-05-31)
      which is titled "fix(INFRA-2329): honor CARGO_TARGET_DIR" — the RED_LETTER changes
      were accidentally bundled into an unrelated CI fix commit
    - `git log HEAD ^origin/main | wc -l` → 50 commits stranded on detached HEAD
    - `git diff origin/main HEAD -- docs/audits/RED_LETTER.md | wc -l` → 621 added lines
      (Issues #12 and #13 content)
    
    Issues #12 and #13 also filed gap YAML files (INFRA-1952, INFRA-1954) that are only
    in the working tree, not in origin/main:
    - `git show origin/main:docs/gaps/INFRA-1952.yaml` → "not found"
    - `git show origin/main:docs/gaps/INFRA-1954.yaml` → "not found"
    
    Additionally: 50 commits of fleet work (PRs #2273 through #2936, dating 2026-05-16
    through 2026-06-01) are stranded on the detached HEAD, never pushed to origin/main.
    
    Root causes (likely):
    1. Cold Water sessions committed to detached HEAD and ran `git push origin main` which
       pushes the `main` branch ref (still at 8afa2e9), not HEAD — a no-op.
    2. CI gates or remote protection rules reject direct pushes to main.
    
    Falsifying condition: If a `git fetch origin` reveals origin/main is further ahead
    than 8afa2e9 (2026-05-16) and contains RED_LETTER Issues #12 and #13.
  acceptance_criteria:
    - "docs/audits/RED_LETTER.md on origin/main contains `## Issue #12` and `## Issue #13`"
    - docs/gaps/INFRA-1952.yaml and docs/gaps/INFRA-1954.yaml are present on origin/main
    - "Cold Water step 6 documents the correct push path for a detached-HEAD environment: `git push origin HEAD:main` or equivalent, verified to reach origin/main"
    - CI test or git hook prevents future stranded-HEAD Cold Water commits (e.g., verify that the push target matches origin/main before committing)
  opened_date: '2026-06-01'
  outcome_id: MISSION-010

