    - "CI smoke test scripts/ci/test-onboarding-browser-wizard.sh: dev server, hit /onboard, assert HTTP 200 + DOM contains all 4 stage cards + verify-button data-attributes."
    - SHIPS AFTER Marcus M-B canonical demo lands. v1 priority is internal operator (Jeff); browser parity is for external evaluators which we are not yet pushing volume to.
    - "Out of scope: full marketing-site polish, demo-data sandbox mode."

