  status: done
  priority: P1
  effort: s
  description: |
    INCIDENT 2026-05-30T15:45-15:46Z: scripts/ops/stale-pr-reaper.sh (INFRA-1410 SLO enforcer) auto-closed 28 in-flight PRs in 60 seconds because they were BLOCKED for >2h30m. The PRs were BLOCKED because TRUNK WAS RED — every PR's required checks (cargo-test, coverage) were failing on a known root cause (chump-integrator test_conflict_aborts_with_structured_error regression). Hotfix PR #2866 was in CI; once it lands, all 28 would have cascade-merged.
    
