    ROOT CAUSE: stale-pr-reaper does not check trunk-RED state before bouncing. INFRA-1410 SLO is meant to flush PRs stuck on their OWN merits (not the queue-wide blocker class).
    
    FIX: stale-pr-reaper.sh must, before bouncing any PR:
      1. Check trunk-RED state (latest run on main, conclusion==failure for cargo-test or similar required-check class)
