      3. If trunk-GREEN but THIS PR has a unique failure (not the same as 5+ other PRs) → proceed with bounce
      4. Add config flag CHUMP_REAPER_HOLD_TRUNK_RED (default ON) for emergency override
    
    Coordination: trunk-red-detector daemon (META-177 Lane C, in PR #2863 — ALSO reaped, now reopened) ships the trunk-RED state file at .chump-locks/trunk-red-detector-state.json. Reaper reads that file.
    
    URGENCY: P0. Daemon currently disabled via launchctl unload. Must ship the trunk-RED gate before re-enabling, OR keep reaper disabled until fix lands.
  acceptance_criteria:
