  effort: m
  description: |
    2026-06-05: 'scripts/coord/bot-merge.sh --gap RESILIENT-103 --auto-merge' ran 21 minutes (pushed the branch but NEVER created the PR) with no self-abort, despite CHUMP_SUBAGENT_BOT_MERGE_BUDGET_S=900s (15min) being documented in CLAUDE.md + SUBAGENT_DISPATCH.md. Two defects: (a) the wall-clock budget is DOCUMENTED but NOT ENFORCED by bot-merge itself — nothing killed the 21-min run; the operator had to pkill it manually. (b) bot-merge does NOT heartbeat the gap lease during a long ship, so the lease expired (02:19:36) MID-SHIP, dropping the gap back to pickable and forcing a lease-less manual push+PR recovery. Net cost: 21min lost + manual recovery + expired lease + a confusing multi-process cleanup.
