    - bot-merge heartbeats the gap lease (chump --heartbeat) at least once per N seconds during the ship so a long-but-progressing ship does not expire its own lease
    - on self-abort bot-merge emits kind=bot_merge_budget_exceeded to ambient.jsonl with elapsed + last-step, and prints the manual-fallback recipe (push + gh pr create + gh pr merge --auto) as its LAST output line so it survives a '
